replies.body:
I was initially on board with the complaints as an Anivia main myself  (wasn’t one that pm’d) until I learned to work with the changes. It’s actually more satisfying to have to be a bit more strategic when using her abilities instead of R E’ing them whenever I felt like it if I outranged them. 

Only thing that would complete me is a visual update on her model and base abilities. A guy can dream. 

{{champion:34}}
